FILE
	/usr/System/sys/helpd.c

NAME
	new_help_file - read help file

PROTOTYPE
	void new_help_file(string path)

CALLED BY
	System, Common, Game

DESCRIPTION
	Read a file ending in .hlp as a help entry and make it
	available for querying.

RETURN VALUE
	Nothing.

ERRORS
	Errors can occur in reading a file or parsing a help entry.

SEE ALSO
	new_help_directory, query_exact, query_exact_with_keywords,
        query_soundex, query_soundex_with_keywords
